%% Detailed current turn/runtime flow.
%% Roadmap status lives only in task_plan.md.
flowchart TD

  Runtime["Runtime package<br>SubstrateAdapter + OperationalContext"]
  Context["OperationalContext<br>domain meaning schema"]
  Substrate["SubstrateAdapter<br>concrete HOW"]
  Registry["CapabilityRegistry<br>contracts filtered by context"]
  Fingerprint["Context fingerprint<br>cache/reuse boundary"]
  Cache["Plan/template cache<br>keyed by context fingerprint"]
  Slice["Compact context slice<br>only when LLM needs it"]
  EvalLadder["Architecture + LLM-path eval ladder<br>sense / cortex / spine / conditional / mission"]
  OrpiManifest["ORPI v0.1 manifest<br>SubstrateAdapter publishes OrpiContracts<br>(+ symbol_mappings / frames / units / risk_policy)"]
  Episode["LabelledEpisode<br>intent / grounding / plan / authority<br>execution / verification / attribution / steering"]
  OrpiConf["ORPI conformance probes<br>contract coverage / manifest-at-init / postcondition<br>cadence / no-LLM-in-loop / labelled-episode"]

  Start["Operator utterance"]
  Station["OperatorStation<br>wrap as CorticalEnvelope"]
  SchemaIn["Schema gate<br>validate typed input"]
  Orch["TurnOrchestrator<br>pending-state check → route intent"]
  IntentCache["Bounded deterministic routes<br>controls / continuations / exact compatibility patterns"]
  LLM["Default semantic router<br>LLM strict JSON-schema OperatorIntent"]
  Fallback["Deterministic compiler fallback<br>visible degraded-availability path"]
  Normalize["Deterministic normalization + IntentVerifier<br>canonical vocabulary / semantic preservation"]
  Intent["OperatorIntent<br>fast or slow path merge here"]
  Dispatch["TurnOrchestrator.dispatch<br>5 knowledge_type paths<br>claim / procedure / provenance / action / control"]
  Mission["MissionCortex<br>MissionContract + validated procedure<br>capabilities / params / lineage"]
  Plan["Cortex<br>build RequestPlan"]
  Snapshot["Representation / Knowledge snapshot<br>current claims + durable procedures"]
  Ready["ReadinessGraph<br>context + contracts + claims + authority"]
  Gate["ApprovedCommand"]

  Runtime --> Context
  Runtime --> Substrate
  Context --> Registry
  Substrate --> Registry
  Context --> Fingerprint
  Substrate --> Fingerprint
  Fingerprint --> Cache
  Context --> Slice

  Start --> Station --> SchemaIn --> Orch
  Orch -->|bounded exact route| IntentCache --> Intent
  Orch -->|otherwise unresolved semantic input| LLM --> Normalize --> Intent
  LLM -. "key / transport / schema failure" .-> Fallback --> Normalize
  Slice -. "compact LLM context if needed" .-> LLM
  Intent --> Dispatch
  Dispatch -->|knowledge_type=procedure/provenance| Plan
  Dispatch -->|knowledge_type=action + compound| Mission --> Plan
  Dispatch -->|knowledge_type=action simple| Plan
  Dispatch -->|knowledge_type=claim/control| Plan
  Plan --> Ready
  Registry --> Ready
  Fingerprint --> Ready
  Cache --> Ready
  Snapshot --> Ready
  Ready --> Gate

  Gate -->|ask / clarify / refuse / answer| Result["CommandResult<br>with provenance"]
  Result --> End["Await next steering"]

  Sense["Sense<br>architecture WHAT"]
  Sense --> SenseHow["SubstrateAdapter<br>sensing HOW"]
  Substrate --> SenseHow
  SenseHow --> Observation["ObservationClaim<br>source + confidence + freshness"]
  Observation --> KnowledgeWrite["Representation surface<br>record evidence + provenance"]
  KnowledgeWrite --> Snapshot

  Gate -->|memory update| MemoryTicket["MemoryWriteTicket"]
  MemoryTicket --> OperatorClaim["KnowledgeBase<br>record durable operator claim/procedure"]
  OperatorClaim --> Snapshot
  OperatorClaim --> Result

  Gate -->|task executable| ExecTicket["ExecutionTicket<br>authorizes mission/runtime entry"]
  ExecTicket --> RuntimeLoop["Cortex runtime loop<br>fresh sense → evaluate mission condition<br>→ choose at most one skill"]
  RuntimeLoop -->|EvidenceFrame| Sense
  Observation --> RuntimeLoop
  RuntimeLoop --> Contract["ExecutionContract<br>one approved skill"]
  Contract --> Spine["Spine<br>execute contract only"]
  Spine --> ActionHow["SubstrateAdapter<br>action/planner/controller HOW"]
  Substrate --> ActionHow
  ActionHow --> ExecClaim["ExecutionReport / ExecutionClaim<br>result + provenance"]
  ExecClaim --> RuntimeLoop
  ExecClaim --> KnowledgeWrite
  RuntimeLoop -->|mission terminal| Result

  Gate -->|explicit motor| MotorTicket["RawMotorTicket"]
  MotorTicket --> Spine
  Spine -->|explicit motor result| Result

  EvalLadder -. "paraphrase equivalence" .-> Intent
  EvalLadder -. "primitive-role checks" .-> Ready
  EvalLadder -. "evidence before action" .-> Sense
  EvalLadder -. "ticket/provenance lineage" .-> Spine

  Substrate -. "publishes capability contracts" .-> OrpiManifest
  OrpiManifest --> Registry
  Result -->|CommandAuthority.record_result projects trace| Episode
  OrpiConf -. "gates contract boundary" .-> OrpiManifest
  OrpiConf -. "no deliberative meta in compiled plan" .-> Ready
  OrpiConf -. "turn round-trips to valid trace" .-> Episode
